data.description: Welcome Home! Let your agent know to write up a offer and send it over. We are presenting offers as they come in. The moment you've been anticipating throughout 2023 is finally here – your journey to homeownership begins with this stunning, light-filled home that exudes both charm and elegance. Boasting three meticulously finished levels, this residence is the epitome of modern living, ready for you to make it your own.  Main Floor Splendor: Step into a world of refined aesthetics as you explore the main floor, where luxurious hardwood floors set the stage. The layout effortlessly combines functionality with style, featuring distinct living and dining areas perfect for entertaining and family gatherings. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, complete with an extended island and a cozy sunroom at the back – a serene spot to soak up the morning light and rejuvenate.  Gourmet Kitchen: Prepare to be awestruck by the gourmet kitchen, a chef's paradise featuring a sleek double oven, stunning granite countertops, and abundant cabinet space. Every detail in this kitchen is designed to inspire culinary creativity and make every meal an occasion.  Upper-Level Oasis: Ascend to the upper level where an oversized loft area awaits, a versatile space for relaxation or play. The four generously sized bedrooms are sanctuaries of comfort, each offering ample space for rest and rejuvenation. The primary bedroom, a true retreat, boasts two walk-in closets and a spa-like bathroom – a private haven to unwind and escape the hustle of daily life.  Basement and More: Venture downstairs to discover a fully finished basement, complete with a full bathroom, offering endless possibilities for entertainment or relaxation. Additionally, take advantage of the extra unfinished space – ideal for storage or to be transformed into your dream home theater.  Your Perfect Home: Spanning over 3,900 square feet, this home is not just a living space; it's a statement of luxury and comfort, waiting for you to start your new chapter. Don't miss this opportunity to turn this house into your forever home.  Schedule your viewing today and step into the lifestyle you deserve!
